---
import CardButton from "../../components/ui/CardButton.astro"
import CardBox from "../../components/ui/CardBox.astro"
import Link from "../../components/ui/Link.astro"
import CardSponsors from "../../components/ui/CardSponsors.astro"
import PageContainer from "../../components/ui/PageContainer.astro"
---

<PageContainer SiteTitle="LAN Party" Heading="LAN Party" SubHeading="Norway Live 2025">

    <div class="w-full h-fit flex justify-center" id="bookings">
        <div class="max-w-[1300px] w-full content-center pt-6 pb-6">
            <div class="flex max-xl:flex-wrap gap-8 max-sm:px-0 max-xl:px-8">
                <div class="width-main flex flex-col gap-8">
                    <CardBox title="Event Details">
                        <p class="text-base">
                            👋 Welcome to our yearly gathering for avgeeks, pilots and virtual air traffic controllers in Oslo!<br>
                            📍 House of Nerds, <Link href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/CjrVuYnguQuNfygz9" target="_blank">Vulkan 18, 0178 Oslo</Link><br>
                            🗓️ 25-27 April 2025
                        </p>

                        <p class="mt-6 mb-4">🪑 To participate in the LAN, you'll need a ticket in advance to reserve a table. Participants under 18 years old are welcome to join us with permission from their guardians.</p>

                        <p class="mb-4">🖥️ Bring your own computer and setup with you. We'll provide both ethernet and wireless internet connections. It'll be possible to rent BenQ Zowie XL2430 24" 144hz monitors, Logitech G203 mice and Svive keyboards from House of Nerds for a fee.</p>
                        <p class="mb-4">🛌 Next door hotel Scandic Vulkan has given us a <Link href="https://www.scandichotels.com/hotelreservation/select-rate?hotel=774&fromDate=2025-04-25&toDate=2025-04-27&room%5B0%5D.adults=1&bookingCode=PROMO15B" target="_blank">discount with this link</Link> for their flex prices. They allow guests between 13-17 years old with parental permission. You're not required to use this accommodation and Oslo offers a lot of alternatives.</p>
                        <p class="mb-4">🚗 Cheapest nearest parking is communal street parking available in the area, or Vulkan P-Hus.</p>
                    </CardBox>
                        
                    <CardBox title="Agenda">
                        <b>LAN Party</b><br>
                        Friday: 18:00–01:00<br>
                        Saturday: 09:00–01:00<br>
                        Sunday: 09:00–20:00

                        <br><br>
                        <b>House of Nerds</b><br>
                        Friday: 16:00–01:00<br>
                        Saturday: 12:00–01:00<br>
                        Sunday: 12:00-23:00

                        <p class="mt-3"><i>More details will be published soon.</i></p>
                    </CardBox>

                    <CardSponsors />
                </div>
                    
                <div class="flex-grow flex flex-col gap-8 width-sidebar">
                    <CardBox title="Documents">
                        <Link class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm mt-2" target="_blank" href="/files/Terms%20and%20Regulations.pdf">Terms and Regulations</Link>
                        <br>
                        <Link class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm mt-2" target="_blank" href="/files/Guardian%20Consent%20Form.pdf">Guardian Consent Form</Link>
                    </CardBox>

                    <CardBox title="LAN Tickets">
                        <p>We are non-profit. The tickets cover expenses related to arranging the event and savings to upgrade equipment in the coming years.</p>
                        <p class="mt-4"><s>
                            <b>Early Bird</b><br>
                            From 300 NOK<br>
                            Available within 1st of March 2025
                        </s></p>
                        <p class="mt-4 mb-4">
                            <b>Late bird</b><br>
                            From 400 NOK<br>
                            Available within 11th of April 2025
                        </p>

                        <CardButton href="https://forms.gle/TYVSk4v57VhtjfoB9" text="Buy tickets" />
                    </CardBox>

                    <CardBox title="Presentations">
                        <p class="mb-4">Are you just passing by to say hello? Check our our presentations on Saturday with free entrance!</p>

                        <CardButton href="/norway-live-2025/presentations" text="Read More" />
                    </CardBox>
                </div>
            </div>                    
        </div>
    </div>
</PageContainer>